methods.booleanAsByte:
Convert booleanValue to a byte.

:param booleanValue: (java.lang.Boolean) - the boxed boolean value to convert to a byte
:return: (byte) booleanValue represented as a byte
methods.byteAsBoolean:
Convert byteValue to a Boolean.

:param byteValue: (byte) - the byte to convert to a boxed boolean
:return: (java.lang.Boolean) the boxed boolean represented by byteValue

text: Utilities for translating boxed Booleans to/from primitive bytes.
